Sands China Shares Rise in Premarket Trading on Loan Agreement

-- B y   S t a n l e y   J a m e s
-- 
2011-09-28T01:22:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/sands-china-shares-rise-in-premarket-trading-on-loan-agreement.html
Sands China Ltd. (1928)  rose 2.8 percent
to HK$22.05 in premarket Hong Kong trading after saying units
Venetian Macau Ltd. and VML Finance LLC entered into a $3.7
billion loan agreement with a group of banks.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stanley James at 
